{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"init"},{"kind":"text","text":"?("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"sourcePosition"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/String"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Index","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS5IndexV","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/String/Index"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"within"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"target"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/String"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A position in a view of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"target","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" parameter.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"sourcePosition","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" must be a valid index of at least one of the views"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"target"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"name":"sourcePosition"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The string referenced by the resulting index.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"target"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If the index passed as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sourcePosition"},{"text":" represents the start of an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"extended grapheme cluster—the element type of a string—then the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"initializer succeeds.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The following example converts the position of the Unicode scalar ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"e\""},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"into its corresponding position in the string. The character at that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"position is the composed ","type":"text"},{"code":"\"é\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" character.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let cafe = \"Cafe\\u{0301}\"","print(cafe)","// Prints \"Café\"","","let scalarsIndex = cafe.unicodeScalars.firstIndex(of: \"e\")!","let stringIndex = String.Index(scalarsIndex, within: cafe)!","","print(cafe[...stringIndex])","// Prints \"Café\""]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the index passed as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sourcePosition"},{"type":"text","text":" doesn’t have an exact"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"corresponding position in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"target"},{"text":", the result of the initializer is","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". For example, an attempt to convert the position of the combining"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"acute accent (","type":"text"},{"code":"\"\\u{0301}\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") fails. Combining Unicode scalars do not have","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"their own position in a string.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["let nextScalarsIndex = cafe.unicodeScalars.index(after: scalarsIndex)","let nextStringIndex = String.Index(nextScalarsIndex, within: cafe)","","print(nextStringIndex)","// Prints \"nil\""],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift","doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/String","doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/String/Index"]]},"varia